**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
**/.turbo
**/src/generated
.git
.github
.vscode
**/*.log

# Local secrets must never enter a build context — without this, COPY steps in the
# Dockerfiles bake whatever .env happens to exist on the host straight into the image layers.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
